    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a dream to drive. She\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-taken care of and ready for many more adventures! Whether you're commuting to work or heading out for a weekend getaway, this car is super reliable and still looks great on the road. I've made sure to keep up with everything, so she's good to go for her next owner. Come take a look, I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 34500.0,
