    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for example of a modern classic that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and performance. This vehicle has been a reliable companion, meticulously maintained with a consistent service history that speaks to its longevity. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor, age-appropriate road wear one would expect from a car that has been enjoyed on the open highway. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is supple with no major blemishes, and every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the engine pulls smoothly and the transmission shifts with precision. Recent service includes a fresh oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection confirming the brakes and tires have plenty of life remaining. This is an honest, dependable car that has been kept in a smoke-free, pet-free environment and is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
