      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Featuring a comprehensive service history and consistent performance standards, it offers an exceptional balance of reliability and long-term value. While exhibiting the natural character expected of a well-cared-for pre-owned motorcar, its structural integrity and mechanical efficiency remain beyond reproach. We invite serious inquiries for this distinguished example of engineering excellence.",
