      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This unit delivers linear power delivery up to its 7,900 RPM redline, paired with a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical integrity is robust, with the critical Vanos system recently serviced and the subframe mounting points inspected and reinforced. Handling is sharp thanks to the factory M-tuned MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension, coupled with a torque-sensing limited-slip differential that ensures optimal traction out of apexes. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains in excellent synchronization, offering the pure analog feedback this chassis is renowned for.",
